a-volta-al-teatro-di-san-carlo-il-balletto-romeo-e-giulietta-nella-versione-di-mikhail-lavrovskij-da-leonid-lavrovskij/' /><link rel='next' title='Rossini, Bellini, Donizetti: &#8220;Romantic songs&#8221; &#8211; Lydia Marimpietri &#038; Ugo Benelli' href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/06/rossini-bellini-donizetti-romantic-songs-lydia-marimpietri-ugo-benelli/' /><meta name="generator" content="WordPress 4.5.3" /><link rel="canonical" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2016/06/der-rosenkavalier-al-teatro-alla-scala-di-milano/" /><link rel='shortlink' href='http://www.gbopera.it/?p=85238' /><link rel="alternate" type="application/json+oembed" href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-json/oembed/1.0/embed?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gbopera.it%2F2016%2F06%2Fder-rosenkavalier-al-teatro-alla-scala-di-milano%2F" /><link rel="alternate" type="text/xml+oembed" href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-json/oembed/1.0/embed?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gbopera.it%2F2016%2F06%2Fder-rosenkavalier-al-teatro-alla-scala-di-milano%2F&#038;format=xml" /><script type="text/javascript">function toggleLinkGrp(id){var e=document.getElementById(id);if(e.style.display=='block')e.style.display='none';elsee.style.display='block';}</script><link rel="stylesheet" href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Carrois%20Gothic:300,400,400italic,700,700italic&amp;subset=latin,cyrillic-ext,cyrillic,latin-ext" type="text/css" /><style type="text/css">h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6{font-family:"Carrois Gothic",Arial,sans-serif}</style><link rel="shortcut icon" href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/favicon.ico"><link href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/themes/wp-pravda/img/icons/apple-touch-icon.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" /><link href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/themes/wp-pravda/img/icons/apple-touch-icon-76x76.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="76x76" /><link href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/themes/wp-pravda/img/icons/apple-touch-icon-120x120.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="120x120" /><link href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp