" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Camilla Simoncini"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/camilla-simoncini/">View all articles by Camilla Simoncini</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2016/06/per-la-prima-volta-al-teatro-di-san-carlo-il-balletto-romeo-e-giulietta-nella-versione-di-mikhail-lavrovskij-da-leonid-lavrovskij/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Per la prima volta al Teatro di San Carlo  il balletto &#8220;Romeo e Giulietta&#8221;  nella versione  di Mikhail Lavrovskij  da Leonid Lavrovskij</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2016/06/rossini-bellini-donizetti-romantic-songs-lydia-marimpietri-ugo-benelli/" rel="next">Rossini, Bellini, Donizetti: &#8220;Romantic songs&#8221; &#8211; Lydia Marimpietri &#038; Ugo Benelli <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2016/06/der-rosenkavalier-al-teatro-alla-scala-di-milano/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sarà pubblicato.</spa